:::Jagger/D'arbanville/Yusef:::

::Three bots were relaxing on Cybertron.  Two were male, and one was female::
Yusef: So listen to this guys.
::he takes out his acoustic guitar and starts playing::
Yusef: It's the latest song ive written.
::The female claps::
D'arbanville: Thats great Yusef!
::The other male, far more powerfully built than Yusef shakes his head::
Jagger: C'mon man, that folky stuff will never fly. Listen to THIS!
::He takes out his electric guitar starts playing his latest power rocker::
Jagger: Now THAT is music!
::D'arbanville smiles::
D'arbanville: That's awesome!
::Yusef and Jagger glare at each other, each one obviously trying to win the 
affection of D'arbanville, while she is oblivious to the feud slowly growing 
between her two best friends::
